Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1

Can you please clarify some concerns on this MP?

The bug description indicates that if transfer-encoding check is present, Glance assumes there is a request body. Also, the header could be anything not just 'chunked'. 

So, we may need to check when the header is invalid or if there is no body in the request and the header is present.
